---
// Plain, calm legal page - see privacy.astro for the same styling notes.
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - Duten Nexa"
  description="The terms governing use of this site and engagements with Duten Nexa."
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="bg-navy py-28 md:py-36">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-5">
      <h1 class="text-h1 text-white">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-faint">Last updated: [NEEDS INPUT: date of legal sign-off]</p>

      <div class="mt-6 rounded-lg border border-teal/40 bg-teal/10 px-5 py-4 text-sm text-teal">
        This policy is pending final legal review.
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-10 text-text-dim">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Using this site</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            You're welcome to read, use, and share it. The content, brand, and design are Duten Nexa's, don't
            republish them as your own.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">What we offer</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            Services described on this site are indicative. Pricing is a starting point; scope, timeline, and
            price are confirmed in a written proposal before any engagement begins.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">No engagement without a signed proposal</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            Reading this site, filling a form, or booking an audit call does not create a services contract. A
            signed proposal does.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Third-party tools</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            We build on top of tools you own, ClickUp, Make, HubSpot, Power BI, and others. Your use of those
            tools is governed by their own terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Limitation</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            We build what we quote. Where we deliver a warranty (spelled out per engagement), we honor it. Beyond
            that, no other warranties are implied. To the extent permitted by law, our liability in any dispute is
            limited to the fees paid for the engagement in question.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Governing law</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            These terms are governed by Nigerian law. Nothing here removes rights you have under the consumer laws
            of your own country.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
            <a href="mailto:admin@dutennexa.com" class="text-teal hover:underline">admin@dutennexa.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
